room_title: Escape room "Zombie Apocalypse" by Escape Zone 60 in Destin
room_description:
The zombie apocalypse is upon us and we desperately need a cure. Your team has been brought in to find that cure in our research facility. Unfortunately, after your team enters the facility and the door locks behind you, you quickly realize you were not brought in to find a cure...
Your team was brought in as test subjects and in 60 minutes a gas will be released into the room. With that knowledge, you will frantically search through everything in the room looking for clues, hints, anything you can find that will ultimately lead to your escape in less that 60 minutes. Do you have what it takes to escape?
